Tadelesh Birra (amụrụ n'ụbọchị 24th April 1975) bụ onye Etiopia na-agba ọsọ ogologo oge. N'afọ 2001, o sonyere na marathon ụmụ nwanyị na 2001 World Championships in Athletics nke emere na Edmonton, Alberta, Canada. Ọ gwụchara n'ọnọdụ nke 31.
O meriri n'ọsọ ụmụ nwanyị na Hannover Marathon na Hannover, Germany na 2003 na 2004. N'afọ 2009, ọ meriri mbipụta mbụ nke Amman Marathon nke emere na Amman, Jọdan.
